    "long_instructions": "##Explain a career you're interested in!\r\n\r\n1. Add a `when clicked` event anywhere in the workspace\r\n2. Snap a `say` block under `when clicked`\r\n\r\n2. Use the same costume for both blocks\r\n\r\n3. Press `Run`, then **click the sprite!**\r\n",
    "start_animations": "{\n  \"orderedKeys\": [\n    \"emoji-happy\",\n    \"emoji-wink\",\n    \"emoji-surprised\",\n    \"emoji-fright\",\n    \"emoji-sunglasses\",\n    \"the-horns\",\n    \"emoji-sleep\",\n    \"bg-default-disco\",\n    \"bg-rainbow-wave\",\n    \"bg-court\",\n    \"bg-texture-green\",\n    \"bg-abstract-blue\",\n    \"bg-abstract-pink\",\n    \"8bg-gradient-green\",\n    \"bg-gradient-pink\",\n    \"bg-gradient-red\",\n    \"bg-gradient-purple\",\n    \"bg-gradient-blue\",\n    \"bg-gradient-orange\"\n  ],\n  \"propsByKey\": {\n    \"emoji-happy\": {\n      \"name\": \"emoji_19_1\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/gamelab/h_LF7PqnHba0BOlL85_9g6TgRHqzd_Lh/category_emoji/emoji_19.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 300,\n        \"y\": 300\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 2,\n      \"version\": \"h_LF7PqnHba0BOlL85_9g6TgRHqzd_Lh\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"emoji\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"emoji-sleep\": {\n      \"name\": \"emoji_02_1\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/gamelab/vaoNISiP9MB6aeAu5TySPtIBPDc9JMLV/category_emoji/emoji_02.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 326,\n        \"y\": 300\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 2,\n      \"version\": \"vaoNISiP9MB6aeAu5TySPtIBPDc9JMLV\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"emoji\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"emoji-surprised\": {\n      \"name\": \"emoji_06_1\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/gamelab/_Xscg5fB95TRoOqlt3745W6Gucfq7NCS/category_emoji/emoji_06.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 300,\n        \"y\": 300\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 2,\n      \"version\": \"_Xscg5fB95TRoOqlt3745W6Gucfq7NCS\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"emoji\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"emoji-wink\": {\n      \"name\": \"emoji_14_1\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1